WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:05.440
CHAPTERS 10-12 OF ISAIAH

00:05.440 --> 00:07.740
This is a LibriVox recording.

00:08.240 --> 00:11.880
All LibriVox recordings are in the public domain.

00:12.280 --> 00:19.320
